---
// CTA.astro - Call to Action promotion banner
---

<section class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-wood-950 via-wood-900 to-wood-950 overflow-hidden border-t border-b border-wood-900/30">
  <!-- Subtle circular lines vector background overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(212,212,44,0.03),transparent_60%)]"></div>

  <div class="max-width-container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 w-full text-center max-w-4xl">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-gold-500 font-bold uppercase block">Una Experiencia Única</span>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-wood-50 leading-tight">
        Afeitá tu Rutina. <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-400 via-gold-500 to-wood-200">
          Tallá tu Verdadero Estilo.
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base text-wood-200 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        No se trata únicamente de cómo salís de nuestro salón, sino de cómo te sentís mientras estás acá. Un sillón de cuero te espera, tu bebida preferida está servida y la navaja ya está lista.
      </p>
      
      <div class="pt-6">
        <a
          href="#booking"
          id="cta-booking-btn"
          class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 overflow-hidden font-semibold text-xs tracking-widest text-wood-950 uppercase bg-gold-500 rounded shadow-xl shadow-gold-500/10 hover:shadow-gold-500/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-gold-400 active:scale-95 group"
        >
          Agendar una Cita Ahora
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
